This creates a simple dropdown.
To create one  dropdown should look like this:
    <div class="dropdown">
        <p class="title item">Pages</p>
        <ul class="dropdown-list">
            <li class="item">Home</li>
            <li class="item">Store</li>
            <li class="item">About</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
Then add an event listener to all the dropdowns (hideDropdown - mouseleave)
and dropdown titles (showDropdown - mouseenter)